title: Bug 116609[Regression]Color orange doesn't work.
OB: When setting the color or background color to orange for a report item, the displayed color is not orange as expected.
EB: The expected behavior is that when you set the color or background color to orange for a report item, the displayed color should be a shade of orange.
SR:
1. Insert a report item.
2. Set the color or background color to orange.
3. Observe the displayed color on the report item.
